name: AVRoutePickerViewDelegate
desc: A protocol that defines the methods to adopt to respond to route picker view presentation events.

items.name: func routePickerViewWillBeginPresentingRoutes(AVRoutePickerView)
items.desc: Tells the delegate that the route picker view will present routes to the user.

items.name: func routePickerViewDidEndPresentingRoutes(AVRoutePickerView)
items.desc: Tells the delegate that the route picker view finished presenting routes to the user.
